title: copy
pid: ba109a3b-febb-4093-9025-04529d1cb33d
body: |2-
  dd bs=4M if=<input file> of=<output file>
  For instance, I most recently ran this (from ~/Downloads):
  sudo dd bs=4M                                                  \
    if=nixos-graphical-19.03.173549.ebdc4419310-x86_64-linux.iso \
    of=/dev/sdb
